Kalpa, or the context.

00:15:20.400 --> 00:15:25.650
When we take care of all
these six aspects of the Veda,

00:15:25.650 --> 00:15:30.050
of knowing, then we are
able to polish our knowing,

00:15:30.050 --> 00:15:32.790
so to speak.

00:15:32.790 --> 00:15:34.690
Some of these seem
to be quite obvious--

00:15:34.690 --> 00:15:35.820
how to make the sound.

