00:19:41.140 --> 00:19:45.060
So we can categorize.

00:19:45.060 --> 00:19:47.170
Some people like to
see the differences--

00:19:47.170 --> 00:19:49.290
how is this different from me?

00:19:49.290 --> 00:19:52.130
And some people like
to see the union-- what

00:19:52.130 --> 00:19:53.230
is there that's common?

00:19:57.340 --> 00:20:01.700
And the last one is
Mimamsa and Vedanta.

