When you get to your
office, you want your things

00:20:10.950 --> 00:20:13.460
in a certain manner.

00:20:13.460 --> 00:20:18.020
If you look at people's desktop,
you probably can make an idea.

00:20:20.820 --> 00:20:25.300
Some people have all kinds of
things put in folders somewhere

00:20:25.300 --> 00:20:27.400
deep down.

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:29.875
And some people have all
their files on the desktop.

00:20:33.540 --> 00:20:38.070
You know, when I was in college,
I used to stay in a hostel.

00:20:38.070 --> 00:20:44.070
And my friend who used to
stay in the next room, one

00:20:44.070 --> 00:20:46.580
day his mother visited.

00:20:46.580 --> 00:20:51.770
She came to his room, and she
saw that it was very creativity

00:20:51.770 --> 00:20:52.270
organized.

00:20:55.120 --> 00:20:57.180
So she thought she
would do him a good turn

00:20:57.180 --> 00:21:00.300
and she arranged everything,
put everything in place,

00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:03.770
folded all the clothes,
put them nicely.

00:21:03.770 --> 00:21:07.902
When he came back, he told-- he
said, Mom, you've spoiled it.

00:21:07.902 --> 00:21:10.690
It's all chaotic now.

00:21:10.690 --> 00:21:14.150
I can't find what is where.

00:21:14.150 --> 00:21:16.400
Some people find order in chaos.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:19.570
Some people find that without
order, there is chaos.

00:21:22.180 --> 00:21:24.280
So when we recognize
these different ways

00:21:24.280 --> 00:21:26.365
of looking at
knowledge, then we're

00:21:26.365 --> 00:21:31.430
able to appreciate the other
person's point of view.

00:21:31.430 --> 00:21:34.830
And to do all this,
first what is required

00:21:34.830 --> 00:21:37.210
is that the mind
needs to be settled.

00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:39.830
And the mind is
so agitated, then

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:44.260
it's very difficult to
perceive all these aspects,

00:21:44.260 --> 00:21:47.050
to appreciate these
other aspects.

00:21:47.050 --> 00:21:51.390
And that's where the techniques
of yoga, the part of yoga,

00:21:51.390 --> 00:21:55.710
evolved as a method
of implementing,

00:21:55.710 --> 00:21:57.470
of acquiring this knowledge.

00:22:03.900 --> 00:22:09.930
If you notice, the whole of our
life, the quality of our life,

00:22:09.930 --> 00:22:12.430
depends in a certain way
on the state of the mind.

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:19.850
We all might be in the same
situation, yet each of us

00:22:19.850 --> 00:22:22.652
reacts to it differently.

00:22:22.652 --> 00:22:24.110
Because each of us
are individuals.

00:22:26.820 --> 00:22:29.850
So if we can do something
about the state of the mind,

00:22:29.850 --> 00:22:32.330
then it makes a
great difference.

00:22:32.330 --> 00:22:35.070
For example, you are here
sitting in front of me

00:22:35.070 --> 00:22:37.090
and hearing, seeing.

00:22:37.090 --> 00:22:37.590
Hopefully.

00:22:41.540 --> 00:22:47.150
And you're listening
to me speaking.

00:22:47.150 --> 00:22:51.930
But if you actually look at it,
the experience of those words

00:22:51.930 --> 00:22:55.220
is happening inside the mind.

00:22:55.220 --> 00:22:59.600
I might touch this podium.

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:02.800
The podium is there, but
what I'm experiencing

00:23:02.800 --> 00:23:03.860
is actually inside.

00:23:03.860 --> 00:23:06.590
The touch happens inside.

00:23:06.590 --> 00:23:08.470
So if you look at
it, all perception

00:23:08.470 --> 00:23:11.090
is actually happening inside.

00:23:11.090 --> 00:23:15.310
Even though, whether the objects
are there outside or not,

00:23:15.310 --> 00:23:17.380
but the experience
of the objects

00:23:17.380 --> 00:23:19.920
is happening in the mind.

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:22.910
And therefore, when
we can have an impact

00:23:22.910 --> 00:23:27.710
on the state of the mind, it can
change the experience, how we

00:23:27.710 --> 00:23:30.060
experience the world outside.

00:23:30.060 --> 00:23:34.370
The techniques of yoga
help us to go into that.

00:23:34.370 --> 00:23:38.730
And that's why, even
though we might not

00:23:38.730 --> 00:23:41.010
be able to change
what is there outside,

00:23:41.010 --> 00:23:43.426
we can definitely change
the experience of that

00:23:43.426 --> 00:23:45.830
which is outside.

00:23:45.830 --> 00:23:48.780
And by changing
that experience, we

00:23:48.780 --> 00:23:52.360
change the way we
interact with the world.

