Have you noticed,
sometimes what people

00:23:55.070 --> 00:23:59.890
say seems to have a great
impact on the state of our mind.

00:23:59.890 --> 00:24:02.720
Someone says something,
we get upset,

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:06.580
and then it takes a long time
for us to come out of it.

00:24:06.580 --> 00:24:10.910
But with these techniques,
we're able to reduce that impact

00:24:10.910 --> 00:24:13.000
and increase these efficiency.

