But at the same time, the
amount of physical activity

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:18.550
that happens in the body,
that seems to have reduced.

00:27:18.550 --> 00:27:22.790
And this imbalance
creates an imbalance

00:27:22.790 --> 00:27:26.000
in our resting patterns in
a certain way, I would say.

00:27:29.170 --> 00:27:31.600
And that's where the
techniques of meditation,

00:27:31.600 --> 00:27:37.350
which enable us to rest deeply,
can make such a big impact

00:27:37.350 --> 00:27:40.940
on our system, that can help
bring back this balance.

